under the **Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0
International License (CC BY-NC-ND 4.0)**.

**Summary:** You may share these assets with attribution, but you may NOT use
them commercially or create derivative works.

Full license text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/legalcode

### Exceptions — Third-Party Assets

Some assets are sourced from third parties and retain their original licenses:

| Source       | License                | Location                         |
|--------------|------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Poly Haven   | CC0 1.0 (Public Domain)| Textures, HDRI (various folders) |
