**ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.**

The narrative content, including but not limited to the story, characters,
dialogues, world-building, factions, and the book **"Integral Pyavitsa"
(Интеграл Пьявица)** by Bruno Arendt, is protected by copyright law.

No part of this narrative content may be reproduced, distributed, or
transmitted in any form or by any means, including photocopying, recording,
or other electronic or mechanical methods, without the prior written permission
of the copyright holder, except in the case of brief quotations embodied in
critical reviews and certain other noncommercial uses permitted by copyright law.

### What this means:
- You may **read** the lore documents in this repository
- You may **not** use the story, characters, world, or lore in your own projects
- You may **not** create derivative works based on this universe
- You may **not** use the names "Project C: The Clouds", "Bruno Arendt",
  "Integral Pyavitsa", or any faction/character names in your own work

For permissions regarding narrative content usage, contact the copyright holder.

